{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2077, "height": 2826, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "上西村前街北坻坞上网", "block_bbox": [749, 226, 1470, 296], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上西村，位于渑池县城东北15公里，因处于方山之余脉——场岭之西，故名岭西村，原场岭之东一村，曰岭东村。后岭东村不复存在，岭西村也只称西村。二十世纪八十年代区划时为区别县南之西村，因此地在我县之北，北为上，故更名上西村。", "block_bbox": [327, 373, 1877, 550], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [149, 738, 232, 1465], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一四七", "block_bbox": [161, 2151, 214, 2261], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上西村乃我杜氏始祖流芳公始迁之地，传承至七世祖芳分居村北，芝分居村南前街，至十世祖廷行之次子林元，四子林川又分居北坻坞上阙，故称西村前街北坻坞上闲支\n", "block_bbox": [329, 564, 1876, 743], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "其世系为：", "block_bbox": [439, 760, 642, 809], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公——忠—果——真金三乐—跃龙——芝一起龙—臻", "block_bbox": [439, 813, 1473, 923], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9326937198638916, "coordinate": [329.209228515625, 564.5722045898438, 1876.402587890625, 743.6760864257812]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9210978746414185, "coordinate": [327.44622802734375, 373.759765625, 1877.53369140625, 550.6614990234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7874698638916016, "coordinate": [439.3087158203125, 813.451171875, 1473.7916259765625, 92